      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a quintessential driver\u2019s spec, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The engine features individual throttle bodies and a cross-bank exhaust manifold for unparalleled throttle response and an 8,400 RPM redline. Mechanically sound, this example has received proactive rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M-variable differential lock, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. Finished in a classic palette with a well-preserved interior, this M3 offers a pure, mechanical connection to the road.",
